         <div type="translation">
            <ab>. . . about them, and ask the most magnificent Count Horigenes, too, on my behalf, about the 500 pounds of pitch and the two gangways; for I wrote to His Illustriousness too about this, but it is necessary for Your Erudition also to remind (him) and give me the answer about these things quickly.
</ab>
